  <article>
    <h1>Program Option 1: Basic Movement Retraining</h1>
    <p>This program is designed for musicians who want to start their retraining with structured, self-guided work complemented by monthly check-ins. It includes custom exercise plans, guidance on how to make your own practice splints, and progress metrics.</p>
    
    <p>We focus on slow-speed movement isolation, postural correction, and sensory discrimination tasks. It provides a solid baseline for retraining without requiring constant direct oversight.</p>

    <blockquote>
      "Ideal for self-disciplined players looking to set up their baseline retraining exercises with professional guidelines."
    </blockquote>
    
